{"article_id":"bbnkQmz6FVM0TRuh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON-Attorney General Jeff Sessions will testify Tuesday before the same Senate committee","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that heard from former FBI Director James Comey last week ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"keeping national attention on a Russia investigation","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that White House officials have been trying to push to the background .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Mr . Sessions earlier this year was forced to recuse himself from the Justice Department ' s investigation of Russian efforts","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to tilt the 2016 election","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"after he belatedly disclosed two meetings with the Russian ambassador to the U.S.","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Comey , during his testimony last week , raised the possibility of other concerns about Mr. Sessions ' s dealings with Russia during the campaign ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Federal Bureau of Investigation leadership before the recusal was \" aware of facts","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that I can ' t discuss in an open setting","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that would make his continued engagement in a Russia-related investigation problematic . \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"In a weekend letter , Mr . Sessions canceled previously planned public testimony before House and Senate appropriations panels .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"that the testimony by Mr. Comey ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"whom Mr. Trump fired in early May ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"made it \" important that I have an opportunity","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to address these matters in the appropriate forum , \"","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"he said","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"was the Senate Intelligence Committee .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"It is unclear whether the intelligence committee hearing will be held in public .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"The Comey appearance dominated a week","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"in which","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"the administration said","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"it had hoped to highlight its stated goal","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"to improve the nation ' s infrastructure .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"This week , President Donald Trump will make expansion of apprenticeship programs the center of his labor policy ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"aimed at filling a record level of open jobs","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"and drawing back Americans","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"who have left the workforce .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The president ' s schedule includes a visit to Wisconsin on Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"where he will stop by a technical college-the same day","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Mr . Sessions is on Capitol Hill .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"But Mr. Trump is helping to keep the Russia probe front and center .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Last Friday , he blasted Mr. Comey in a joint news conference with the Romanian president .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"In a tweet Sunday morning , Mr. Trump called Mr. Comey \" cowardly \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"for asking a friend to tell reporters about conversations","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"he had with the president .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"During those conversations , Mr. Comey said","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Mr. Trump had talked about the investigation of former national security adviser Mike Flynn ' s ties to Russia","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"and had said ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"\" I hope","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"you can let this go. \"","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"The president denies having done that .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"\" I believe","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"the James Comey leaks will be far more prevalent","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"than anyone ever thought possible , \"","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"Mr. Trump said Sunday morning .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"\" Totally illegal ?","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Very ' cowardly ! ' \"","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Many legal experts say","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"there was nothing illegal about Mr. Comey ' s actions ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"given that the material wasn ' t classified","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and that he was no longer a government employee .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. Comey testified last week","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that he asked his friend to share the content of the conversations","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"so it might prompt the appointment of a special counsel ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"which it did ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"when former FBI Director Robert Mueller was named to the post .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s tweets are drawing rebukes even from people in his own party .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"\" I think","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"the worst problem","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"this president has in this instance","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"is the president himself , \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"former Rep. Mike Rogers","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"( R. , Mich. )","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"said Sunday on CNN .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"\" If he would stop talking about the small-ball individual tweets ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"attacking Director Comey personally ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"we could get beyond this . \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"( R. , S.C. ) ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"speaking on CBS ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Mr. Trump was obstructing his own agenda .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Addressing Mr. Trump directly ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Mr. Graham said :","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"\" You may be the first president in history","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"to go down","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"because you can ' t stop inappropriately talking about an investigation","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"if you just were quiet ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"would clear you . \"","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"But part of the Trump legal strategy is to call into question Mr. Comey ' s credibility .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Jay Sekulow , a member of Mr. Trump ' s legal team , pointed to statements","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"regarding the FBI investigation of Hillary Clinton ' s use of a private email server while secretary of state .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"\" James Comey ' s credibility has been brought into question on multiple occasions during the Clinton investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and here ultimately the special counsel has to weigh that","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"as he does his investigation , \"","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Mr. Sekulow said Sunday on ABC .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Mr. Comey has defended his handling of the Clinton email probe .","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"Beyond his contacts with Russian officials , Mr . Sessions also may face questions","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"about why he didn ' t do more","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"to shield Mr. Comey ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"who worked for him ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"from Mr. Trump ' s private outreach .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Mr. Comey told the Senate panel","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that the president had Mr . Sessions and others leave the room","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"so he could talk to Mr. Comey alone ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"and that is when Mr. Trump allegedly pressured him on the Flynn investigation .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Mr. Comey also said","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"he later appealed to Mr . Sessions","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"to ensure","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"that he would not again be left alone with Mr. Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"but that Mr . Sessions didn ' t respond .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"A Justice Department spokesman rejected that characterization","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Mr . Sessions told Mr. Comey","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"the agency needed to be careful about \" following appropriate policies \" regarding such contacts .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Mr . Sessions was a vocal advocate for Mr. Trump during the 2016 campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"and his staffers and former aides have taken jobs in the White House and across the administration .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Still , Mr. Trump was upset","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"after Mr . Sessions recused himself from the Russia probe ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"one White House official said .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"The president ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"who has denied any involvement with Russia election hacking ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"viewed Mr. Sessions ' s decision as a sign of weakness ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"the official said .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Mr . Sessions is also expected to face Senate questioning","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"about why he was involved in firing Mr. Comey","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"given that he had recused himself from questions","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"related to Russia .","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"As FBI director , Mr. Comey was overseeing that investigation .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"In an interview with NBC News last month , Mr. Trump said","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"he was thinking about \" this Russia thing \"","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"when he decided to fire Mr. Comey ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"but the White House initially cited a recommendation for termination by Mr . Sessions and a deputy attorney general","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"based on Mr. Comey ' s broader job performance .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"( D. , N.Y. )","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"said Sunday","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"that this is one of several questions","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"Mr . Sessions should be asked to answer","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"it should be done in a public session .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"\" The president said","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"Comey was fired","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"because of Russia .","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"How does that fit in with his recusal ?","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"It doesn ' t seem to stand up well to me , \"","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Mr. Schumer said on CBS .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"The attorney general also drew some criticism from Democrats for the en masse firings of U.S. attorneys ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"including Preet Bharara in Manhattan , earlier this year .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Mr. Bharara said Sunday on ABC","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"that Mr. Trump called him three times","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"following his election","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"and fired him less than a day","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"after he refused to return the third call from the newly elected president .","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"\" It appeared to be that he was trying to cultivate some kind of relationship , \"","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Mr. Bharara said in the TV interview .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"-Michael C. Bender and Aruna Viswanatha contributed to this article .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":305,"left":304,"right":152,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":174,"right":303,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":164,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":156,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":154,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nucle